  "description": "The horizon is where drift meets FM — OscA classic sawtooth for the tonal center, OscB in FM mode tuned to a fifth above. As drift moves OscB away from its fifth, the harmonic relationship continuously updates. A compound migration across the perfect fifth interval.",
